ANALYSIS.NAME: ICP_CEC_AGTU_V
ANALYSIS.DESCRIPTION: CEC bepaling in AgTu extract op vaste matrix

CALCULATION.SOURCE_CODE:
LOI_W = LOI / 20 'waarde van LOI om af te wegen massa te schatten
If (LOI_W < 2.5) then Gewicht = 2 Elseif (LOI_W > 2.5) and (LOI_W < 4.5) then Gewicht = 1 ELSE Gewicht = 0.5 ENDIF
Return Gewicht

'omrekening van mg/l naar cmol+/kg'
Teller = 30 * Calcium Noemer = Gewicht * 1000 * 2004 / 100 cmol = Teller / Noemer * 100
Return cmol

'berekenen van de berekende CEC'
SampleProduct = select sample.product_grade
if (SampleProduct = "QC_VAST") then 'de berekening wel uitvoeren zonder resultaat van de voorbehandeling voor QC samples CEC_AGTU = 1 Return CEC_AGTU endif
CEC_AGTU = CA + K + MG + NA + AL + FE + MN
Return CEC_AGTU

' omrekenen naar droge stof
originalSample = select sample.original_sample
sampletype = select sample.sample_type where sample_number = originalSample order by sample_number
AnalysisName = "DS_OVEN_105" AnalysisComp = "DS.105"
DS105 = select result.numeric_entry where sample_number = originalSample and analysis = AnalysisName and name = AnalysisComp order by sample_number
if (isNull(sampletype) or (sampletype = "DUP")) then if (isEmpty(DS105)) then RETURN endif else Subroutine("FN_COMPCALC_DS_CORRECT") 'returns dscorrectie DS105 = 1000 * dscorrectie endif
Ca_DS = (CA / DS105) * 1000
Return Ca_DS
